ing: 1/4 cup canned garbanzo beans, rinsed and drained
des: "This is a light and quick lunch choice."
ins: Spread avocado on one slice of toasted pumpernickel bread.  Place garbanzo beans on top of avocado and sprinkle with salt.  Top with prosciutto, tomato, Havarti cheese, and alfalfa sprouts.  Top with another slice of bread to make a sandwich.
